menu "WellD Zigbee"

    config WELLD_ZIGBEE_CHANNEL_MASK
        hex "Zigbee channel mask"
        default 0x07FFF800
        help
            Bitmask of channels to scan during network steering.
            0x07FFF800 = all 2.4 GHz channels (11-26).
            Single channel examples: ch11=0x00000800, ch15=0x00008000,
            ch20=0x00100000, ch25=0x02000000.

    config WELLD_ZIGBEE_SEND_DELAY_MS
        int "Post-send delay before sleeping (ms)"
        default 2000
        range 500 5000
        help
            Time the Zigbee stack stays alive after sending the report,
            giving the coordinator time to acknowledge. Reduce to save
            battery; increase on slow or congested networks.

endmenu
